## Pre-Task Protocol

1. **Always start with** @INDEX.md - Review the document index for relevant
   documentation
2. Read @system-overview.md for system understanding
3. Identify specific documents needed from the Quick Task Lookup table in the index
4. Consult product documents from docs/product
5. Consult technical references docs/tech

## Post-Task Protocol

1. Update the single authoritative source for any changed information
2. Update cross-references if new relationships are created
3. Mark task completion in @progress.md
4. Update @INDEX.md if new documents are created
